## ðŸ”Ž Nickname / Identity Search (Name)
Tools for checking for accounts by nickname and matching identities.

- [WhatsMyName](https://whatsmyname.app/) â€” bulk check of nicknames on hundreds of platforms.

- [Namechk](https://namechk.com/) â€” quick search for available nicknames and domains.

- [Namecheckup](https://namecheckup.com/) â€” search by social services and domains.
- [MIT PGP Keyserver (pgp.mit.edu)](https://pgp.mit.edu/) â€” Search for public PGP keys by address/name.

