## ðŸ“ž Phones
Tools for reverse number lookup, carrier verification, and validation.

- [FreeCarrierLookup](https://freecarrierlookup.com/) â€” carrier and country identification by number.

- [PhoneValidator](https://www.phonevalidator.com/) â€” number validation, format, and provider.

- [411 Reverse Phone Lookup](https://www.411.com/reverse-phone-lookup) â€” reverse phone number lookup (US/Canada).

